巾」是內地6至14歲少年加入少年先鋒隊後在學校期間佩戴的標誌。其形狀為紅色三角形，長約90厘米。佩帶方式與領帶結相似。少年先鋒隊章程解釋稱，「紅領巾代表紅旗的一角，是革命先烈的鮮血染成，每個隊員都應該佩戴它和愛護它」。</strong>"},{"pid":"fc00524393a5c518e5f273e63c2f8c9a632a4c3d","tid":2287209,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T14:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Ac55Ny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Ac55Ny.jpg&h=b317fab6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09dde454f42a53c8045f4c716dc4a0acfb8d9367","tid":2287209,"uid":279326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"敵將is doctor lee<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/vampire_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4c28fdb76f4b01ee4a5fec1b082e369fd871e8","tid":2287209,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80438c18beb2d68eda5688ee3b2d3d8ff3d2c7c3","tid":2287209,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:32:57.000Z","msg":"可以去見毛主席，做少先隊隊長，好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9af6a71578c8d8e540348c4e6157142a2566ce","tid":2287209,"uid":39010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:35:03.000Z","msg":"唔係比人勒死 點意外法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d930ba94d80b63d59d07bb7c9399147bc7ffc5","tid":2287209,"uid":10890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:35:21.000Z","msg":"紅領巾代表紅旗的一角，是<del>革命先烈</del><span class=\"red\">自己</span>的鮮血染成，每個隊員都應該佩戴它和愛護它"},{"pid":"46defc37e507e5da6390e066514419461047f0a1","tid":2287209,"uid":17859,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:38:10.000Z","msg":"先五年級啫 快快趣刷過首抽做歐美人好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}